(43, 2, 16, 24, 7, 11, 11, 'my Father’s house', 'House of God and Corruption', 'Both passages emphasize the corruption of God''s house. John 2:16 refers to the house as a place of merchandise, while Jeremiah 7:11 describes it as a den of robbers.', 'theme', 0.489, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
